Questions¶

1. Top 5 stores in terms of sales¶

3. Relation between area visibility and sales¶

Q1: Top 5 stores in sales¶

In [ ]:
# creating a new df grouped by outlet_identifier
df_top5 = df.groupby(["Outlet_Identifier"]).sum()
In [ ]:
df_plt = df_top5["Item_Outlet_Sales"].sort_values(ascending=False)
In [ ]:
plt.bar(df_plt.index,df_plt.values)
fig = plt.gcf()
fig.set_size_inches(12, 8)
plt.title('Top 5 Stores in sales')
plt.xlabel('Outlet identifier')
plt.ylabel('Sales values')
plt.show()
